Module.module_desc:
Integrates with MailChimp to show a person's status on a MailChimp List and also allows for convenient one-click subscribe/unsubscribe functionality. (Subscribing a person this way still requires that they opt-in via the email they receive from MailChimp).
This module depends on: - MailChimp 1.1 API DLL (MailChimp_v1_1.dll) - CookComputing.XmlRpcV2.dll - A lookup type which contains all the MailChimp Lists with these values and qualifiers. * Lookup value: the Name of the List/Newsletter * Qualifier 1: MailChimp ListID * Qualifier 2: corresponding Arena NewsletterID (int) * Qualifier 8: Background image URL to use when displaying newsletter status for the person.
